{
  "stem": "11797.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 77.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw the bayonet, I put my stomach in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must have been three inches before it hit me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they went out in a huff.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Said, no Jews here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- they are-- they were-- there were Latvians there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was all different kinds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they-- when-- mostly-- they were mostly guards for beating Jews, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were mostly guards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "German soldiers, German SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were in combining with the German army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not the regular army, but with the SS or the Gestapo or the SD or the some other or the commanders that were in charge of the concentration camps, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did they behaved?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They behaved like animals.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They behave like there's nobody else in the world except them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were in charge of the world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody had power.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody had no-- no-- there was nothing to say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, they behaved like they wrote the constitution for the world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I stayed in that ghetto a while until my father had a passport from Buenos Aires.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] on the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], it's like an order.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you have any kind of passports for any country, like, especially Buenos Aires, America, Brazil, anyplace, please register yourself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You'll be got out-- sent back to the country where your passport is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father had a passport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before the war, I think I mentioned that he was in Buenos Aires.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he came back because my mother didn't want to go there because she was afraid to go to Buenos Aires because my grandmother told her not to go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because she was the only daughter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She didn't want to lose my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
